	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64565981"><p>Regarding alleged DEI quotas, I've been on hiring committees. It's clear to me people prefer to hire clones of themselves when the qualifications are roughly equal. It's not necessarily blatant racism, probably just social comfort.</p><p>Thus, left to their own devices, it will be a constant mitosis of the good-ol-boy network (GOBN). DEI quotas might be an ugly fix, but without them, GOBN lives on and on.</p></div>
	</div>

